title.narrative: Professional Evidence and Applied Knowledge Services

description.narrative: This activity (Professional Evidence and Applied Knowledge Services) is a component of Professional Evidence and Applied Knowledge Services reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £8,865,823. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Education policy and administrative management, Health policy and administrative management, Public sector policy and administrative management, Social Protection, Business Policy and Administration, Environmental policy and administrative management, Research/scientific institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, DAI Europe, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 01-06-2012 and the end date is 30-09-2016.
